# 🚀 MySpace

> *Let's explore the universe together!*

A social network with a space theme, allowing users to register, log in, create posts, follow other users, and interact with publications.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 **Authentication** — Registration and login with form validation
- 📝 **Posts** — Create posts with title, content, and optional image
- ❤️ **Likes** — Like/unlike posts
- 👥 **Follow** — Follow and unfollow other users
- 📊 **Statistics** — View account stats
- ⚙️ **Settings** — Account configuration
- 🌌 **Animated space background** — Parallax star background

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
MySpace/
│
├── index.html              # Start page (login / register)
├── homePage.html           # Main page (feed, navigation)
│
├── style/
│   ├── startPage.css       # Start page styles
│   ├── homePage.css        # Home page styles
│   ├── starBackground.css  # Animated star background
│   └── starButton.css      # Animated galaxy button component
│
├── scripts/
│   ├── scripts.js          # Auth logic (register, login, localStorage)
│   ├── startPage.js        # Start page interactions (password visibility)
│   └── homePage.js         # Home page logic (posts, likes, follow, stats)
│
└── images/
    └── astro.jpg           # Default profile picture
```

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

No installation or build step required — this is a pure HTML/CSS/JS project.

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/myspace.git
   cd myspace
   ```

2. **Open in your browser**
   ```bash
   # Simply open the start page
   open startPage.html
   ```
   Or serve it locally with a tool like VS Code Live Server.

> ⚠️ The app uses `localStorage` to persist user data. No backend or database is required.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Usage |
|---|---|
| HTML5 | Page structure, `<dialog>` for modals |
| CSS3 | Animations, CSS Grid/Flexbox, CSS variables |
| Vanilla JavaScript | DOM manipulation, localStorage |
| Google Fonts — *Zen Dots* | Space-themed typography |

---

## 🌠 Pages

### `startPage.html` — Landing Page
- Welcome screen with registration and login buttons
- Modal dialogs for both forms
- Full form validation with inline error messages
- Password visibility toggle

### `homePage.html` — Main Application
- Left sidebar: user profile, navigation (Feed, Follow, Statistics, Settings)
- Center: post creation form + scrollable feed
- Right sidebar: user discovery panel

---

## 💾 Data Storage

All data is stored in the browser via `localStorage`:

| Key | Description |
|---|---|
| `users` | Array of all registered users |
| `currentUser` | Currently logged-in user object |

Each user object:
```json
{
  "id": 1718000000000,
  "nom": "Dupont",
  "prenom": "Lina",
  "mail": "lina.dupont@example.com",
  "pp": "<base64 image>",
  "mdp": "password",
  "follow": [],
  "like": []
}
```

---

## 🎨 Design

- **Color scheme:** Deep space dark (`#0c0c17`) with white contrast
- **Font:** [Zen Dots](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Zen+Dots) for titles
- **Buttons:** Custom animated galaxy buttons (via `starButton.css`)
- **Background:** Multi-layered animated star parallax (`starBackground.css`)

